Tlen xoxohuic cahqui [[ichin]] tlaltihpahtle, ti quin tocayotia cuauhmeh, [[xihuitl]], [[zácatl]], ihuan cequime mo miahtia ican tlen itoca toctzintle. Inon toctle panquiza ichin xōchitl. 

Tlen xoxohuic qui pia xōchitl axan quilia magnoliofitas. 

Xōchitl tic tocayotia ce tlamantle mozcaltia ichin xiuhmeh, canin mo temaca tlen itoca mihtiliztli.

